      "date": "2015-02-11 19:57:21.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified+1\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/090d06b0-b227-11e4-9c8b-5254006e85c2).  Ran 16 tests.  No failures.",
